            S5_2_2 --> S5_2_3[5.2.3 - Analyst: Develop stress case using Phase 2 downturn scenarios]:::llmPartial
            S5_2_2 --> S5_2_4[5.2.4 - Analyst: Develop bull case assumptions]:::llmPartial
            S5_2_3 --> S5_2_5
            S5_2_4 --> S5_2_5
            S5_2_5[5.2.5 - Analyst: Run sensitivity analysis on key credit variables]:::llmPartial
        end

        S5_1_OUT --> S5_2_1

        S5_2_OUT[Phase 5.2 Output: Base, stress, and bull cash flow models with sensitivity tables]:::output
        S5_2_5 --> S5_2_OUT

