        S5_2_OUT --> S5_3[5.3 - Analyst: Build recovery analysis with trough valuation and liquidation waterfall]:::llmPartial
        S5_2_OUT --> S5_4[5.4 - Analyst: Model debt service waterfall by seniority]:::llmPartial
